Package com.gmail.mohitsainiknl2.mscalculator.theme

Class DefaultTheme

java.lang.Object
com.gmail.mohitsainiknl2.mscalculator.theme.DefaultTheme
All Implemented Interfaces:
Theme
public class DefaultTheme
extends java.lang.Object
implements Theme
DefaultTheme is the default Color theme for this Calculator. This class implements the Theme interface, So, this class must define all methods declared in such interface.
